description.en: Learn to code. Build projects. Earn certifications. Since 2015, 40,000 graduates have gotten jobs at tech companies including Google, Apple, Amazon, and Microsoft.
description.ga_IE: Foghlaim le cód.Tionscadail a thógáil.Deimhnithe a thuilleamh.Ó 2015, tá 40,000 céimí tar éis poist a fháil ag cuideachtaí ardteicneolaíochta lena n-áirítear Google, Apple, Amazon, agus Microsoft.
